# Email Configuration for Discovery Form
# Get these credentials from your email service provider

# Gmail Configuration (recommended for development/small-scale)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-specific-password

# For Gmail, you need to:
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Google Account
# 2. Generate an App-Specific Password at https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Use that password as EMAIL_PASSWORD

# Alternative: Use other email services like SendGrid, Mailgun, etc.
# Modify the server/api/send-discovery-email.post.ts file accordingly
